      among other things. i have no grudges, no detrimental past, no handicaps physically or mentally or anything like that. i feel like i have an obligation to save the world.

      i want to learn and be great for my own self but i dont know, i feel like the world will end without my contributions.

      but i am not quite an adult - it is only a matter of months before i am and i know nothing about the adult world i have heard so much about. what's it like, moving out and finding a job and all that other stuff.

      also i really like your music. :-)
